newsitem.title: SINGAPORE: Singapore bunkers slip on healthy supplies.
newsitem.headline: Singapore bunkers slip on healthy supplies.

text.p: Singapore bunker indications on Monday were quoted lower as supplies were healthy amid poor enquiries, traders said.
They said cst 380 prices were quoted between $121-$123 per tonne. Bunker 180-cst were quoted around $126-$128 per tonne.
A major said he had sold a cargo of cst 380 at $121.50 per tonne. Prices have softened, tracking lower cargo levels, said a trader.
MDO prices were steady, indicated between $210-$220 and gas oil steady at $230-$235.
